-- Sky Solar, Sigdo Koppers to Announce Chile Project
-- B y   M a t t   C r a z e
-- 2012-06-27T18:28:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-27/sky-solar-sigdo-koppers-to-announce-chile-project-correct-.html
(Corrects company name in headline and first paragraph in
story originally published on June 25.)  China’s Sky Solar Holdings Co. and
Chilean engineering company Sigdo Koppers SA will sign an
agreement to build 300 megawatts of solar projects in the South
American country, Chile’s government said in an e-mailed
statement today.  Sky Solar and Sigdo Koppers will announce the $900 million
deal tomorrow in the presence of Chinese Premier  Wen Jiabao , who
will visit Santiago as part of a South American tour.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Matt Craze at 
 mcraze@bloomberg.net  